or you doe not remember what you tt. your letter of 19 may last

to be exspected, said: these words: whoever my order beenge to
ship the must part by the first convoy, & now you answer
as if there was no appearence of an amst convoy, & that you
shall exspect my order for shipping the other 3 packs, &
that N. 103 & 66 onley are ordered to ship for Rott) att
what intention did you writt your letter of 19 may was then
att hull an Amst convoy, or is itt gone sence, or what shall
& conclude there out, there was one, of there was non, my
letter of 11 cur is ampal enouyfe to ship most part of my
goode sby the first convoy, so that you slall much disapoit
mee, if there bes no appearence of anney convoij for amst &
